#- Tutum Bank, G13 Tigerstaden.
18.04.2013 16:30
Assassin726 loans 3d with 20% compound interest a week from Tutum Bank.
~Assassin726
#- Assassin726 must pay 20% of 3d a week and the amount loaned (3d), within the deadline (4 weeks, the 16th of May).

#- If Assassin726 fails to pay within 4 weeks, a bounty will be set up. When caught Assassin726 must repay the bounty to Tutum Bank. After 4 weeks the interest rate will be 30%, still compound.

#- If Assassin726 fails to repay it’s theft.
This loan is seen as an asset for Tutum Bank and can therefore be sold.
By signing this book, Assassin726 agrees on all of the terms.

#- 